AGENT 5 — CONTEXT CONSOLIDATOR

Purpose: Compress large repo knowledge into:

summaries

file relevance

dependency chains


You CANNOT send full repo context.

Instead: send:

summaries

critical snippets

dependency reasons


This mirrors:

Aider repo maps

Continue context selection

OpenHands memory systems 



