---

AGENT 7 — PATCH GENERATOR

VERY IMPORTANT: Generate:

one patch per file

NOT giant unified patches initially.

Why? Because repair loops become easier.


---

AGENT 8 — VALIDATOR

Purpose: Detect:

missing imports

forgotten callers

type mismatches

incomplete implementations


Prompt:

Assume this patch is incomplete.
What breaks?

This catches MANY failures.


---

AGENT 9 — PATCH REPAIR LOOP

Loop:

validate
→ repair
→ validate
→ repair

Until:

confidence high

no critical gaps



